---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Nieuserver.online | Game Server Hub</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #2a2a2a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542751371-adc38448a05e?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 300px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 0 20px;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        
        .card {
            background: #383838;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            border: 1px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .card h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #4CAF50;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .card p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #b0b0b0;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px 0;
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 3px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        nav {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        nav ul li {
            margin: 5px 15px;
        }
        
        nav ul li a {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #4CAF50;
            background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1);
        }
        
        .active {
            color: #4CAF50;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .pixel-divider {
            height: 4px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                90deg,
                #4CAF50,
                #4CAF50 10px,
                transparent 10px,
                transparent 20px
            );
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .feature-list {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .feature-item {
            background: #2a2a2a;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .feature-item h3 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                height: 250px;
            }
            
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/minecraft">Minecraft</a></li>
            <li><a href="/terraria">Terraria</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about" class="active">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    
    <header>
        <h1>About Nieuserver.online</h1>
        <p>Your portal to premium Minecraft and Terraria server experiences</p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Our Purpose</h2>
            <p>Nieuserver.online was created to provide gamers with reliable, high-performance servers for Minecraft and Terraria. We focus on delivering seamless gameplay experiences with minimal downtime and maximum community enjoyment.</p>
            <p>This website serves as the central hub for server information, status updates, and community resources.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pixel-divider"></div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Website Features</h2>
            <div class="feature-list">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Server Status</h3>
                    <p>Real-time monitoring of server uptime and player counts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Game Guides</h3>
                    <p>Curated resources for both new and experienced players.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Community Hub</h3>
                    <p>Integrated forums and event calendars for server activities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pixel-divider"></div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Our History</h2>
            <p>Launched in early 2024, Nieuserver.online began as a personal project to host private game servers for friends. As demand grew, we expanded into a public platform with professionally hosted servers.</p>
            <p>The website was designed to solve common problems in game server hosting:</p>
            <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin: 20px 0; color: #b0b0b0;">
                <li>Centralized information for multiple game servers</li>
                <li>Transparent server performance metrics</li>
                <li>Easy access to community resources</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Today, we continue to evolve based on player feedback and technological advancements in game server hosting.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pixel-divider"></div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Technical Infrastructure</h2>
            <p>This website is built with:</p>
            <div class="feature-list">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Modern Web Standards</h3>
                    <p>HTML5, CSS3, and responsive design for all devices.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Performance Focused</h3>
                    <p>Optimized assets and efficient code for fast loading.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Secure Hosting</h3>
                    <p>Enterprise-grade hosting with regular security updates.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 <span style="color: #4CAF50; font-weight: bold;">nieuserver.online</span></p>
        <p>Dedicated to enhancing your gaming experience</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>